{"tid":2307823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平主持政治局會議  一個月內第三度提備戰打仗","createTime":"2020-12-01T12:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T04:25:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf1c2b4bf262851f00cbebe79d2a9aaa5a6fe32","tid":2307823,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2815000/2816775/202_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2815000%2F2816775%2F202_1024.png&h=f4436ae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美角力白熱化、且普遍預期中美關係難因拜登上台顯著改善之際，中共總書記習近平周一（30日）主持中共政治局會議，審議軍隊政治工作條例，重申黨的領導，並要求聚焦聚力備戰打仗。這是中央層級在不足一個月內，第三度提及備戰打仗。<br />\n<br />\n根據新華社發布的通稿，周一召開的中共中央政治局會議，合共審議了「軍隊政治工作條例」、「中國共產黨統一戰線工作條例」、「中國共產黨黨員權利保障條例」等3項條例。但具體條文內容並未公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2816775/%E7%BF%92%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%B1%80%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%20%C2%A0%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A6%E6%8F%90%E5%82%99%E6%88%B0%E6%89%93%E4%BB%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2816775%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%2520%25C2%25A0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2582%2599%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%2589%2593%25E4%25BB%2597&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0olFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=34ef74e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2816775/%E7%BF%92%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%B1%80%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%20%C2%A0%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%BA%A6%E6%8F%90%E5%82%99%E6%88%B0%E6%89%93%E4%BB%97</a>"},{"pid":"f80d1280b39e97bce56abeebc44d8eabb15a2051","tid":2307823,"uid":59501,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202